data.title: Embassies and consulates by destination
data.text: This directory contains contact information for government offices that provide consular services to Canadian citizens abroad. Not all government offices provide full consular services. This directory also includes Australian and Swedish offices around the world that, by special agreement, provide consular services to Canadians. For up-to-date, detailed information on a particular office, visit that officeâ€™s website or contact it directly.
